:wave: Good Afternoon

We're constantly looking to improve and hear from this great community of builders! Some of you may have received this in an email from me if you were in the alpha, but I'd love as much feedback as possible.

And while the link below is regarding our dev docs beta, my ears are wide open for anything related to API limits, APIs, CLI, sdks, permissions, or getting started with our builder experience on HubSpot.
